===Noun===
{{en-noun|corrigenda}}

# An [[error]] that is to be [[correct]]ed in a [[print]]ed work after [[publication]].
# {{label|en|usually|in the plural}} A [[list]] of errors in a printed work as a separate page of [[correction]]s, known as an [[errata]] page.

